title: Molika Cafe and Bakery
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bakery and cafe specializes in Le Brea bakery style naturally leavened bread. Small selection of breads (mostly ciabatta and foccacia) available daily. For custom orders for a larger selection and/or to order two-pound loaves, place order at least one day prior to pick-up. Cafe has vegan options. Owner speaks fluent English and Spanish.
